&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Organization Summary: &lt;/strong&gt;BBYO is the leading pluralistic, Jewish teen movement and has been providing exceptional leadership programs and identity enrichment experiences for 100 years. We offer year-round activities in hundreds of local communities and inspiring world-wide travel experiences enabling teens to explore areas of leadership, service, civic engagement, Israel education and Jewish values. Learn more about BBYO at &lt;a href=&quot;https://azabbg.bbyo.org/&quot;&gt;https://azabbg.bbyo.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;International August Executives Conference:&lt;/strong&gt; (August Execs) is an annual gathering of the highest-elected teen leadership (President) from every community to plan, train, get ready for the year ahead, vote on legislation, and finalize skills and strategies for their home regions and communities. This experience is filled with exclusive training, unique workshops, and world-class experts. Learn more about August Execs Conference at &lt;a href=&quot;https://azabbg.bbyo.org/experiences/august-execs&quot;&gt;https://azabbg.bbyo.org/experiences/august-execs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
