&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;: Fairfax, VA, U.S.A.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work Commitment: &lt;/strong&gt;Tuesday, August 11 – Sunday, August 16, 2026&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stipend / Remmuneration:&lt;/strong&gt; $400 + Travel (if applicable)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Position Responsibilities include (and are not limited to):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
