&lt;li&gt;A community-wide Seattle J-Serve initiative&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A regular series of teen service activities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordination and facilitation of two 2-weeks SJCC CIT sessions during the summer of 2027&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Staffing select SJCC events as part of the Community Engagement team (i.e. shabbat dinners, holiday festivals, camp counselor programs during the school-year) &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
