&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Salary:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;$75,000-$85,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At BBYO, we’re motivated by our mission, inspiring us to reimagine work to make it fun, flexible, and fulfilling. We are looking for a passionate Senior Manager, Grants and Donor Engagement to join our Marketing Team and make a difference. As the Senior Manager, Grants and Donor Engagement, you will help advance BBYO’s mission by strengthening the systems, stories, and communications that support philanthropic giving. This role is centered on writing and coordinating seven-figure foundation grants, helping frontline fundraisers stay on top of regional grant deadlines, drafting strategic messages from CEO to major donors, and supporting donor engagement efforts. The ideal candidate is an excellent writer, natural storyteller, and highly organized project manager who can turn BBYO’s impact into clear, compelling communications that inspire generosity and deepen donor relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SHAPING THE FUTURE FOR TEENS AND YOURSELF&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Manager, Grants and Donor Engagement, a typical day will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;padding-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MAJOR GRANTS AND GRANT COORDINATION (60%)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;padding-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;In partnership with the CEO, members of the leadership team, and BBYO’s fundraising professionals, write, coordinate, and oversee major grants, including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing the full lifecycle of foundation grants, including proposal preparation, submission, reporting, and renewal tracking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drafting, editing, and&amp;nbsp;submitting&amp;nbsp;grant proposals and reports that align with funder guidelines and organizational priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reviewing, editing,&amp;nbsp;and strengthening&amp;nbsp;key&amp;nbsp;regional grant&amp;nbsp;submissions&amp;nbsp;as needed in partnership with fundraisers, helping ensure&amp;nbsp;they&amp;nbsp;are clear, compelling,&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;submitted&amp;nbsp;on deadline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinating with program, finance, and other staff to gather required data, budgets, testimonials, and narratives for grant applications and reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tracking and updating grant calendars, deadlines, and deliverables to ensure compliance and on-time submissions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining&amp;nbsp;accurate, up-to-date records in the grants database and CRM, ensuring data integrity across the full portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing the grants inbox,&amp;nbsp;monitoring&amp;nbsp;incoming requests and updates,&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;routing information to the&amp;nbsp;appropriate team&amp;nbsp;members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sending reminders to fundraisers and internal partners to ensure regional grants, reports, and supporting materials stay on track&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;padding-left: 40px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;STRATEGIC COMMUNICATION AND DONOR ENGAGEMENT (40%)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage BBYO’s direct mail program, including planning, drafting, coordinating approvals, tracking timelines, and partnering with internal and external stakeholders to successfully execute five&amp;nbsp;initiatives&amp;nbsp;per year&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft&amp;nbsp;key&amp;nbsp;communications from CEO to major donors, ensuring messages are&amp;nbsp;timely, polished, mission-driven, and aligned with BBYO’s voice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support donor engagement efforts, helping prepare materials, messaging, briefings, and follow-up communications that inspire giving&lt;/li

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;BBYO AND PHILANTHROPIC ENGAGEMENT IN PERSPECTIVE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245417&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;BBYO is&amp;nbsp;seeking&amp;nbsp;a talented, driven, and entrepreneurial fundraiser to serve as Senior Vice President of Philanthropic Engagement—an extraordinary&amp;nbsp;leadership&amp;nbsp;opportunity at a&amp;nbsp;pivotal moment&amp;nbsp;when both the need and the potential for impact have never been greater. BBYO sits at the center of a rapidly evolving Jewish landscape, increasingly serving as the primary&amp;nbsp;pluralistic&amp;nbsp;platform for post–bar/bat mitzvah engagement and leadership development for Jewish teens.&amp;nbsp;The challenge ahead is to translate that impact into sustained philanthropic investment that fuels BBYO&#39;s growth and shapes the future of Jewish communal life.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245417&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is not a traditional development role.&amp;nbsp;The&amp;nbsp;Senior Vice President&amp;nbsp;will inherit—and be expected to activate—a powerful set of assets:&amp;nbsp;relationships with some of the leading Jewish philanthropists in North America, a global alumni community numbering in the hundreds of thousands, a track record of expanding impact, and a network of highly committed volunteers&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;board members.&amp;nbsp;BBYO currently&amp;nbsp;operates&amp;nbsp;an annual campaign of $25 million with a Centennial Campaign that seeks to increase endowment commitments to $100 million&amp;nbsp;over the next three years.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245417&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The successful candidate will capitalize on significant investments in BBYO&#39;s fundraising infrastructure, including a recently enhanced database and prospect management ecosystem, to&amp;nbsp;identify&amp;nbsp;new opportunities for growth and deepen donor engagement. Through compelling storytelling, strategic relationship-building, data-informed decision-making, and sophisticated cultivation strategies, this leader will expand BBYO&#39;s philanthropic reach and drive transformational support for the organization&#39;s mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245417&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;BBYO offers the rare chance to take on a meaningful fundraising challenge with the resources, partnership, and platform needed to achieve truly outsized results.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245417&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;THE JOB&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134245417&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;As a Senior Vice President, Philanthropic Engagement a typical day will include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;1342454

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BBYO is always interested in meeting new applicants!&amp;nbsp; Whether you&#39;d like to work in our International Office in DC or in one of our regions, we would like to review your resume.&amp;nbsp; While we are not currently hiring please submit your resume here and we will be in touch with you if your experience matches our openings in the future.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Who we are:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt; We&#39;re a global network of passionate professionals excited to make a difference in the lives of Jewish teens. We are the Jewish community&#39;s largest and fastest growing pluralistic platform for reaching and inspiring Jewish teens during the school-year with 600 teen-led local chapters and over 100 weekend retreats along with a plethora of summer experiences including Israel visits, global travel programs, and leadership camps. We work as a strong and inclusive team and every day is different by design. We are fast-paced, high energy and results driven.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BBYO offers fantastic benefits!&amp;nbsp; In addition to excellent health care and retirement benefits, we offer generous vacation and sick time plus 9 paid secular holidays as well as paid time off for the Jewish holidays.&amp;nbsp; We provide excellent opportunities for professional development. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BBYO Camp Nurse&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Various Locations&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Organization Summary&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;: &lt;/strong&gt;BBYO is the leading pluralistic, Jewish teen movement and has been providing exceptional leadership programs and identity enrichment experiences for more than 90 years. We offer year-round activities in hundreds of local communities and inspiring world-wide travel experiences enabling teens to explore areas of leadership, service, civic engagement, Israel education and Jewish values. Learn more about BBYO’s summer and travel programs at &lt;a href=&quot;http://bbyo.org/teens/experiences/summer&quot;&gt;bbyo.org/teens/experiences/summer&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Chapter Leadership Training Conference (CLTC)&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; is a 13-day program designed to develop and strengthen the leadership skills of BBYO chapter leaders.&amp;nbsp;At CLTC, teens from across North America will form mock chapters and learn specific skills that help them lead their chapter at home.&amp;nbsp;CLTC builds on a curriculum based on teens focusing on leadership development, program planning, and hands-on experience. CLTC is expected to reach 500 teens across 4 sessions throughout the summer.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;International Leadership Training Conference (ILTC)&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; is a 19-day program designed to hone leadership skills for teens serving (or aspiring to serve) as regional BBYO position-holders in their home communities. ILTC participants often become the top leaders of the BBYO teen movement, gaining skills in recruitment, program planning and civic engagement. ILTC is expected to reach 200 teens.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Kallah&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; is a 3-week Jewish learning and spirituality institute that inspires teens to explore their Jewish identities and interests in a diverse, pluralistic setting encouraging questioning and experimentation. Kallah participants gain important Judaic skills and come away feeling a deeper connection to Jewish study, Israel and community. Kallah is expected to reach 200 teens.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
